# Mokwon University Computer Science Department Website Clone

## Project Structure
The project follows a standard web development structure:

- `index.html` - Main entry point of the website
- `css/` - Contains all stylesheet files
- `js/` - Contains JavaScript files
- `images/` - Contains all image assets

## Key Features
The website includes the following main sections:
- Department Introduction
- Faculty Information
- Academic Programs
- Student Activities
- Community/News
- Contact Information

## Development Guidelines
1. Maintain responsive design for all screen sizes
2. Follow Korean language support requirements
3. Ensure accessibility standards are met
4. Keep consistent styling with the original website

## File References
- Main stylesheet: [style.css](mdc:css/style.css)
- Main JavaScript: [main.js](mdc:js/main.js)
- Main HTML: [index.html](mdc:index.html)

## Navigation Structure
The website uses a hierarchical navigation system with:
- Top-level navigation for main sections
- Secondary navigation for subsections
- Mobile-responsive menu system

## Assets Organization
- Images should be optimized for web use
- Maintain consistent naming conventions
- Use appropriate image formats (JPG for photos, PNG for graphics)
